Class SurveyResultController

  • java.lang.Object
    • SurveyResultController
  • public class SurveyResultController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a controller for the SurveyResultView. It contains fields for the survey title and the view. There are methods to get the results for a survey title, and add XChart pie charts to the view based on the results.
    See Also:
    SurveyResultView, Question, Survey, ResponseDatabaseHelper, SurveyDatabaseHelper

    • Method Detail

      • getResults

        private void getResults()
        Connects to both the Question and Response databases to retrieve results for a survey. Gets the question strings and stores the results for each question in a Map of answer strings and the corresponding number of responses for that possible answer. calls generateCharts to display the results
